{"tid":1630792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真討論) 林鄭似係想令示威者變成恐怖分子","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T18:55:51.000Z","uid":193015,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd43f437490df5c1b1f7ec5f46e4fd7ea657da03","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"佢整條蒙面法出黎<br />\n從係想激大家做得激進d<br />\n<br />\n佢就可以大條道理做咩都得<br />\n<br />\n中立嗰d有機會真係覺得示威者過份左"},{"pid":"aa394359bebc4b68551dea47551b2181a6835f69","tid":1630792,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1141853f16843ed941cdee48b1b8bceec8ddfdd5","tid":1630792,"uid":295637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都要推"},{"pid":"7bc55dcb018144dbd186e2602618fffb988a5c35","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe29084dd6d507c2d35d5c171f1641dfeac9149d","tid":1630792,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"04077243225dd2dd53bf5cea5d2512f1776c5498","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n真心似林鄭做法"},{"pid":"3c97ce9fff09c1d6565cf450e2e0d9385a3530d5","tid":1630792,"uid":299611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"我都推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c0ccffc4ed6e467b46abaa7e1f0c7db5cd6ad0","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dfdfd13abb62560e551b538681592337c69df76","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17fb1d81bce6c277a40ced86a8d29a92b869bad8","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"028659c0c806c096c83c14d387725a0068728180","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e1ac177bea19e022f221cc7f85dac0eaad12fff","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6830210d32e5df02ce09ab628188958eaeb88fc","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"要慢慢打<br />\n<br />\n林鄭好明顯想快end game"},{"pid":"cf8a69bc548e9cfaf786d1427ede990885ffb7f7","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:50:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭推蒙面法後一日<br />\n故意激香港人, 等你地示威<br />\n<br />\n而POPO一開頭冇點理<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好明顯係想向外界特顯示威者既'暴力'</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而佢叫人割席, 亦都係想特顯勇武派<br />\n另更多人覺得係破壞社會<br />\n<br />\n一來等外界以為示威者成真暴徒<br />\n二來可以試下香港人底線<br />\n三來佢可以順理成章咁做佢之後想做既事<br />\n<br />\n例如推更多惡法, 凍結資產... ...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係我小小分析<br />\n我覺得文宣好重要"},{"pid":"6e9683483745df3b33df78d805bc276acd533fb0","tid":1630792,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}